aptive devices) to operate a computer keyboard, mouse, and other computing equipment The incumbent must spend long hours in intense concentration Stress may be caused by the need to complete tasks within tight deadlines EDUCATION: Minimum requirement: undergraduate degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering or Information Technology other related field from an accredited university.     DISCLAIMER: An equivalent combination of education and experience, which results in demonstrated ability to apply skills will also be considered. Pythian is an equal opportunity employer.  All applicants will need to fulfill the requirements necessary to obtain a security check.  Desired Skills and ExperienceQUALIFCATIONS: The position requires specialized knowledge and experience in performing the following: Experience in backend and web-UI development Strong proficiency in Python language and specifically Django framework as well as web data scrapping and processing Strong understanding of procedural and object-oriented design and development Experience with Adobe Flex and Adobe Flash Builder Knowledge of XML, and JSON Comfortable working in Linux environment Solid understanding of database concepts and design techniques with practical experience in relational database, preferably MySQL and Oracle Experience with version control systems, preferably Git Experience with browser-side JavaScript Knowledge of SQL Perl is a bonus Knowledge of NoSQL technologies such as MongoDB or HBase is a bonus Knowledge of Hadoop is a bonus Experience with cloud infrastructure such as Amazon Web Services is a bonus Past contributions to open source projects is a bonus Pythian doesn't measure seniority just based on years of experience but rather by the individual abilities to be productive and "do the right things" PERSONAL ATTRIBUTES: Ability to discuss and present complex technical solutions Attention to detail and high level of accuracy Strong organizational and time management skills/Ability to set priorities and meet deadlines Ability to work with minimal supervision Excellent oral and written communication skills About this companyPythianIn a data-driven world, organizations depend on Pythian’s peerless expertise to ensure they always have secure, reliable access to the business-critical information they can’t do without. Serving retailers, financial institutions, online entertainment companies and organizations in specialized sectors like healthcare, Pythian keeps even the most complex data infrastructures ‘always on’ and optimized for peak performance. Our team of top-tier database experts provides design, monitoring, migration and tuning services for all types of production environments, including Oracle, MySQL, Microsoft SQL Server and NoSQL. Headquartered in Ottawa with offices around the globe, Pythian offers a unique, flexible contracting model that allows clients to cost-effectively access the very best database support when and how they need it.Other jobs at PythianGreater New York City AreaGreater New York City AreaNorthland, New ZealandSimilar jobsHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 5 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 20 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoThis is a preview of the Software Developer job at Pythian. To view the full job listing, join LinkedIn - its free!Join LinkedIn - its free!People also searchedPeople also viewedHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 5 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 20 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 days agoHyderabad Area, IndiaPosted 11 